  {
    "Id": 8,
    "Content": "\n### Installation from Deb package\n\nTo install Nutty from the `.deb` package make sure you have installed all the above execution dependencies of Nutty (no need build dependencies). Then run the below command",
    "ContentSha": "GPeG+NZgKGwtyjDbf8EFuuolD7C1BxmbYsUReQNrrNo=",
    "SectionType": "",
    "StartLine": 0,
    "EndLine": 0,
    "Translation": "\n### 从 Deb 包安装\n\n要从 `.deb` 包安装 Nutty，请确保已安装上述所有 Nutty 的运行时依赖（无需构建依赖）。然后运行以下命令",
    "Status": "ok",
    "RowTranslations": [],
    "IsCodeBlock": false
  },
  {
    "Id": 9,
    "Content": "```bash\nsudo dpkg -i <deb-package-name>.deb\n```",
    "ContentSha": "ZWRf9uK0XUXL1qOddtZCPaw0HXt3Mg6V/tyvg0COq3Y=",
    "SectionType": "",
    "StartLine": 0,
    "EndLine": 0,
    "Translation": "```bash\nsudo dpkg -i <deb-package-name>.deb\n```",
    "Status": "ok",
    "RowTranslations": [],
    "IsCodeBlock": true
  },
  {
    "Id": 10,
    "Content": "\nAnd to uninstall Nutty installed via `.deb` package run",
    "ContentSha": "WXZ2qExbBKYL73yWaW7Y7bLqklGguW2HbYgshXx0b5M=",
    "SectionType": "",
    "StartLine": 0,
    "EndLine": 0,
    "Translation": "\n要卸载通过 `.deb` 包安装的 Nutty，请运行",
    "Status": "ok",
    "RowTranslations": [],
    "IsCodeBlock": false
  },
  {
    "Id": 11,
    "Content": "```bash\nsudo apt autoremove com.github.babluboy.nutty\n```",
    "ContentSha": "MTLXQTM5mBH7amW3sQt1W2PM+7ZWrK+zok0EGAcyCug=",
    "SectionType": "",
    "StartLine": 0,
    "EndLine": 0,
    "Translation": "```bash\nsudo apt autoremove com.github.babluboy.nutty\n```",
    "Status": "ok",
    "RowTranslations": [],
    "IsCodeBlock": true
  },
  {
    "Id": 12,
    "Content": "\nIf you want to directly build the `.deb` package of Nutty yourself then install the above build dependencies and then run",
