    "SectionType": "",
    "StartLine": 0,
    "EndLine": 0,
    "Translation": "如果您想直接构建 Nutty 的 `.deb` 软件包，请先安装上述构建依赖项，然后运行\n",
    "Status": "ok",
    "RowTranslations": [],
    "IsCodeBlock": false
  },
  {
    "Id": 13,
    "Content": "```bash\ngit clone https://github.com/babluboy/nutty.git\ncd nutty\ndpkg-buildpackage -us -uc\ncd ..\n```",
